  "title": "A Toast Before the Fleet Departs",
  "summary": "On the observation deck of The Mission's headquarters in Trinumvira on Caspar, the Tarasar family hosts a farewell party as elements of the Caspian 4th Fleet prepare to leave for the Charros System. Admiral Lynae Cassius arrives with her cadet son Andrev, mingling with Crestian Tarasar, the Kubaz designer Zubindi, the venture capitalist Malif, and the naval hostess Nara, while Axel Vichten attends at the head of a delegation of Noques Rasala priests. Over wine and barbed banter about uniform colors, ranks, and Corellian liquor, Axel reconnects with Lynae and meets his godson Andrev, encouraging the boy's ambition to join the starfighter corps. Crestian's daughter Atsvara cheerfully bluffs the bartender into serving her drinks. The gathering remains warm and convivial, an evening of diplomacy and old friendships on the eve of the fleet's deployment.",
